Package: inferencer
Type: Package
Title: Simple Unified Wrappers for Hosted Foundation Model Inference
        APIs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(
      given = "Oliver",
      family = "Zhou",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      email = "olee7149@gmail.com"
    )
Author: Oliver Zhou [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Oliver Zhou <olee7149@gmail.com>
Description: Provides lightweight R wrappers for querying and listing models
    from several hosted foundation model inference platforms, currently
    including Google Gemini, Groq, OpenRouter, and Cerebras. The package is
    designed for simple prompt-based workflows and quick experimentation,
    with minimal abstraction and a consistent interface across providers.
    It includes helper functions for model discovery and text generation,
    while leaving room for future support of provider-specific parameters
    and advanced options.
